Class ResourceDataAccessException

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ResourceReadException, ResourceWriteException

    public class ResourceDataAccessException
extends java.lang.RuntimeException
    A Java RuntimeException indicating a problem accessing (e.g. reading/writing) the data of the target Resource.
    Since:
    1.3.1
